'''2021年[[世界短道速滑锦标赛|世界短道速滑锦标赛]]'''于2021年3月5日至7日在荷兰多德雷赫特进行<ref name="announcement"/>。

比赛开赛时，全球依旧受[[2019冠状病毒病疫情|2019冠状病毒病疫情]]困扰，为防止感染扩大，赛事主办方出台了相应的措施，包括限制相关人员与外界的接触、强制相关人员在规定场合下佩戴[[口罩|口罩]]、要求相关人员在赛前接受[[2019冠状病毒病检测|病毒检测]]等。<ref name="announcement"/>

受疫情影响，[[中国|中国]]、[[日本|日本]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.tokyo-sports.co.jp/sports/figure-skating/2668161/|script-title=ja:フィギュア世界選手権はどうなる？ ショートトラック世界選手権派遣を見送り|publisher={{lang|ja|[[東京體育|東京スポーツ]]}}|date=2021-01-26|accessdate=2021-03-07|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126162417/https://www.tokyo-sports.co.jp/sports/figure-skating/2668161/|archivedate=2021-01-26}}</ref>、[[韩国|韩国]]、[[英国|英国]]等队伍均放弃参加该届世锦赛。<ref>{{cite news |last1=Morgan |first1=Liam |title=China and South Korea withdraw from World Short Track Speed Skating Championships |url=https://www.insidethegames.biz/articles/1104971/china-south-korea-withdraw-short-track |access-date=2021-03-05 |work=Inside the Games |date=2021-03-04 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210304163924/https://www.insidethegames.biz/articles/1104971/china-south-korea-withdraw-short-track |archivedate=2021-03-04 }}</ref>另外，部分队伍也仅能派出水平较低的选手参赛<ref>{{cite web|url=https://sports.yahoo.com/top-short-track-speed-skating-181357848.html|title=Top short track speed skating nations to miss world championships|publisher=Yahoo!Sports|date=2021-02-20|accessdate=2021-03-08|archiveurl=https://archive.is/V3lIN|archivedate=2021-03-08}}</ref>。

由于[[国际体育仲裁法庭|国际体育仲裁法庭]]于2020年12月17日作出判决，禁止存在[[俄羅斯體育禁藥|国家级体育禁药问题]]的[[俄罗斯|俄罗斯]]在两年内以国家名义参加国际大赛<ref>{{cite web|url=https://apnews.com/article/russia-banned-name-flag-olympic-games-a8bd342806883f66152859701d5ae5d4|title=Russia can't use its name and flag at the next 2 Olympics|first=Graham|last=Dunbar|date=2020-12-17|access-date=2020-12-17|publisher=[[美联社|Associated Press]]|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201217152124/https://apnews.com/article/russia-banned-name-flag-olympic-games-a8bd342806883f66152859701d5ae5d4|archivedate=2020-12-17}}</ref>，该队在该赛事以“俄罗斯滑冰联盟”（{{lang|en|Russian Skating Union}}，缩写：{{lang|en|RSU}}）的名义参加比赛<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.olympicchannel.com/en/stories/news/detail/short-track-suzanne-schulting-double-gold-dordrecht-saturday-worlds/|title=Suzanne Schulting takes double gold at Dordrecht Worlds|publisher=[[奥林匹克频道|Olympic Channel]]|date=2021-03-07|accessdate=2021-03-07|archiveurl=https://archive.is/dXPle|archivedate=2021-03-07}}</ref>。

